summary.purpose: Provides red and yellow crane SVG icon generator functions conforming to the VehicleSvg signature for use as map markers and menu icons.
summary.problem_solved: Supplies the crane vehicle type's red (ignition off) and yellow (idle) icon variants. Green and gray crane variants are in cranes2.tsx.

exports.name: redCraneIcon
exports.description_one_line: Returns a red crane SVG element with configurable size, site colour, CSS class, and viewBox context.

exports.name: yellowCraneIcon
exports.description_one_line: Returns a yellow crane SVG element with configurable size, site colour, CSS class, and viewBox context.

symbols.name: redCraneIcon
symbols.description_one_line: Returns a red crane SVG element with configurable size, site colour, CSS class, and viewBox context.

params.name: width
params.description: Width attribute for the SVG element.

params.name: height
params.description: Height attribute for the SVG element.

params.name: siteColor
params.description: Fill colour for site-specific colour accents.

params.name: className
params.description: CSS class name applied to the SVG element.

returns.description: Red crane icon SVG element. Red indicates ignition is off.

details.what_it_does: Generates a detailed crane SVG icon in red, indicating the crane vehicle's ignition is off (parked/stopped).

minimal_correct.title: Render a red crane icon
minimal_correct.code:
import { redCraneIcon } from 'akeyless-assets-commons';

const icon = redCraneIcon('30', '30', '#FF0000', 'newIconCar', 'map_icon');

symbols.name: yellowCraneIcon
symbols.description_one_line: Returns a yellow crane SVG element with configurable size, site colour, CSS class, and viewBox context.

params.name: width
params.description: Width attribute for the SVG element.

params.name: height
params.description: Height attribute for the SVG element.

params.name: siteColor
params.description: Fill colour for site-specific colour accents.

params.name: className
params.description: CSS class name applied to the SVG element.

returns.description: Yellow crane icon SVG element. Yellow indicates idling.

details.what_it_does: Generates a detailed crane SVG icon in yellow, indicating the crane vehicle is idle (ignition on, not moving).

minimal_correct.title: Render a yellow crane icon
minimal_correct.code:

const icon = yellowCraneIcon('30', '30', '#FFFF00', 'newIconCar', 'map_icon');
